2 - Overview of the Mautic dashboard
Quick overview of the Mautic dashboard
Mautic can be customised with
 - Themes
 - Plugins

With social monitoring you can monitor your Social Media accounts

3 - Installing the tracking pixel
A couple of ways to add tracking pixel
Similar to Google Analytics
JS will need to be added
Wordpress is used but Joomla or Drupal is very similar
Go to settings (right side of page cog logo)-> configuration -> Landing Page Settings
You can add the JS manually following the instructions or Mautic has its own WP plugins
Use the Mautic Community plugin
You will need add your url in your Mautic plugin settings


